<field>CUSTOMER</field>
<desc>
            <p>Denotes the CUSTOMER for whom the loan preferences are being captured.</p>
            <p />
            <p>Validation rules</p>
            <p />
            <p>1-6 numeric character Customer Code.</p>
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>GROUP.CREDIT.LIMIT</field>
<desc>
            <p>Captures the option if Group Credit limit needs to be setup. </p>
            <p />
            <p>Validation rules</p>
            <p />
            <p>Allowed values are None, No or Yes. Optional input. By default it is None.</p>
            <p />
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>LIAB.CUST.ID</field>
<desc>
            <p>Captures the liable Customer.</p>
            <p />
